seo: 冰蝎3,流量解密,AES,Base64,加密流量,解密工具
summary: 该插件用于解密冰蝎3的AES+Base64加密流量，并计划后续支持冰蝎4及其它加密方式（如Xor、magic）的解密，同时还将推出哥斯拉和冰蝎的密钥爆破插件。
summary_en: This plugin is used to decrypt BingScorpion 3 AES+Base64 encrypted traffic and plans to support decryption of other encryption methods (such as Xor, magic) in the future. It will also launch key cracking plugins for Godzilla and BingScorpion.
